  "sketchCode": "// Example: LCD 16x2 Hello World\n// Display text and a running counter on an LCD.\n\n#include <LiquidCrystal.h>\n\nLiquidCrystal lcd(12, 11, 5, 4, 3, 2);\n\nvoid setup() {\n  lcd.begin(16, 2);\n  lcd.print(\"Hello, World!\");\n}\n\nvoid loop() {\n  lcd.setCursor(0, 1);\n  lcd.print(\"Time: \");\n  lcd.print(millis() / 1000);\n  lcd.print(\"s  \");\n  delay(500);\n}\n",
